On behalf of our valued client, CBRE is excited to present to the market for sale via Expressions of Interest, 12 Trade Street, Lytton. This prime investment opportunity is situated within the tightly held Industrial hub of Lytton which is part of the Southern Tradecoast area. Lytton is located approx. 19klms from the Brisbane CBD, approx. 12klms from the Brisbane Airport and on the doorstep of the Port of Brisbane. This area is very popular amongst a number of logistics and distribution occupiers due to its key infrastructure and location; some of these users include K-Mart, Yusen Logistics, Silk, Toll, Toyota just to name a few.


This site is improved by a 1,540sqm office/warehouse facility which offers the following key features:


•	370sqm recently refurbished office accommodation split over two levels
•	1,170sqm warehouse split over three individual buildings
•	4,223sqm General Industry zoned site
•	Large concrete hardstand for external storage/container set down
•	36% site cover (approx)
•	Value add opportunity 
•	Fully fenced and secured site
•	Property offers huge exposure to Port of Brisbane Motorway


This property is being offered For Sale via Expressions of Interest closing Thursday 5th March 2020 at 4pm AEST. (If not sold prior).

For further information regarding this prime port investment or to arrange your inspection, please contact Exclusive Agents, Zac Ryan or Ben Lyons of CBRE.

Lytton Industrial Estate is one of the most desirable and sought after estates within the Southern Tradecoast and is ideal for warehousing and transport businesses. Lytton adjoins the Port of Brisbane and provides easy access to the Gateway Arterial and Brisbane Airport.

This prime 1,654sqm freestanding office/warehouse sites on regular shaped 4,007sqm allotment. It offers corporate office space split over two levels and provides a high bay clearspan warehouse with significant hardstand for additional storage and container set down area.


The property features the following:

- 1,440sqm high bay, clearspan warehouse

- 6 electric container height roller doors
- Fully concreted 4,007sqm site area offering providing easy truck access and significant hardstand
- 360sqm awning for undercover loading/unloading
- Fully fenced and secured site
- Three (3) phase power supply
- Available early 2017

For more information or to arrange your inspection, please contact Exclusive Agent Ben Lyons from CBRE.

CBRE is excited to present to the market for sale via Expressions of Interest closing Wednesday 17th April 2019 at 4pm, 98 Benjamin Place, Lytton. This is an opportunity to secure a high quality, corporate, industrial office/warehouse with secured income.

98 Benjamin Place is located in the highly sought after suburb of Lytton on the doorstep of the Port of Brisbane. This location offers excellent access on and off the Port of Brisbane Motorway which connects directly on the Gateway Motorway. 

The property incorporates approximately 400sqm of well-appointed office accommodation split over two levels. The concrete tilt slab construction, insulated warehouse, boasts an impressive internal roof height up to 11.4 metres providing excellent cubic capacity. Easy truck access is offered via its four container height roller doors.
